pan><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> of the WHO [ii]. Within two weeks of beginning homeopathic treatment in 2007 in a high-risk area of Cuba, a 90% decrease of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Leptospirosis</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> was observed in the homeopathic intervention area (over 2 million people), whereas in other low-risk areas which did not receive any treatment the disease rates continued to rise. Homeopathic prophylaxis has since then been extended to the entire Cuban population (11 million plus), and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Leptospirosis</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> is reported to be now almost eradicated. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt 5pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">2)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">In the light of this and a myriad of other evidence positive for homeopathic treatment, homeopathy provision is spreading more and more widely around the world, most recently in Arab countries. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt 5pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">3)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">A previous UK Science &amp; Technology committee found homeopathy to be but a ‘placebo treatment’, apparently omitting in the process large amounts of conclusive evidence to the contrary (including effects of homeopathy not only on humans, but also on animals, plants and live cells in test tubes). As David </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Tredinnick</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> MP is aware, an enormous and ever-expanding body of pro-homeopathy evidence has in any case come out since the S&amp;T Committee meeting in 2010.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt 5pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">4)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Two online polls on the future of the Glasgow homeopathic hospital stand currently at just over 2,000 votes to close it, over 18,000 votes to save it [iii]. The public understands the value of homeopathy.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">              </span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt 5pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">5)</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">RECOMMENDATION.  In the light of potentially catastrophic effects on the whole human race, the present S&amp;T committee has an obligation to ignore homeopathy nay-</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">sayers</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and denigrators and to recommend others to do likewise; instead to demand implementation of existing homeopathic research and to encourage still more. </span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">REFERENCES</span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">[</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">i</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">]  </span><a href="http://hpathy.com/homeopathy-papers/some-history-of-the-treatment-of-epidemics-with-homeopathy/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:none">http://hpathy.com/homeopathy-papers/some-history-of-the-treatment-of-epidemics-with-homeopathy/</span></a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-